{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "Until December 1, it is still possible to register your innovative product, service or chain concept for the Agribusiness Award. Complete the registration form today.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "> “By participating, you are forced to look at your own innovations through the eyes of someone else.”", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "Jury chairman Agribusiness Awards, Director and professor of Retail & Entrepreneurship", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "In an earlier interview with [Boerenbusiness](https://www.boerenbusiness.nl/artikelen/10914505/kijk-door-ogen-van-ander-naar-je-eigen-informatie) jury chairman Laurens Sloot encouraged companies in the agri and food sector to participate. \"It broadens your network and a strong network promotes innovation.\" The director of EFMI Business School and part-time professor of Retail & Entrepreneurship at the University of Groningen joined the jury of the [Agribusiness Award](http://agribusinessaward.nl/) last year.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "Companies that want to register their innovation for the Agribusiness Award 2026 must take a number of [conditions] into account (http://agribusinessaward.nl/regulations). As jury chairman, Sloot mainly looks at how innovative and distinctive the innovation is. But also whether it is mainly an idea or a concept or whether the innovation has already proven itself. \"And we look at whether there is a potentially strong revenue model. Something will only fly if companies can actually earn something from it.\" The reason for Sloot to contribute to the Agribusiness Award is the impact that the election makes.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "> “With the great visibility of the Agribusiness Award, it is not only a compliment to the winning company, but also a calling card for the sector as a whole.”", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "Jury chairman Agribusiness Awards, Director and professor of Retail & Entrepreneurship", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "His advice to companies that want to register their innovation: \"Dare to open up. By participating in the Agribusiness Award you are forced to look at your own innovations through the eyes of someone else. You also broaden your network and new things will automatically come your way. People like to think along and a strong network promotes innovative capacity.\"", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0012", "text": "Do you have an innovative product, service or chain concept that deserves a podium? Then register for the Agribusiness Award 2026. Registration closes on December 1, 2025, so go to [www.agribusinessaward.nl](http://www.agribusinessaward.nl/) and complete the registration form.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0012", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 12, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 12}}
{"id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0013", "text": "## Read more stories from entrepreneurs in the agricultural sector", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium__a2-late-chunking__0013", "source_slug": "laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium", "source_title": "Final call for Agribusiness Award - innovations deserve a podium", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/ondernemersverhalen/agrarisch/laatste-oproep-agribusiness-award-innovaties-verdienen-een-podium.html", "source_date": "2025-11-19", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "ondernemersverhalen", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 13, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 13}}
